headline: HomeServe South Jersey and Lennox Team Up to Give Back Through Feel the Love Campaign
summary: STRATFORD, N.J., October 15, 2025--HomeServe South Jersey partnered with Lennox in annual Feel the Love program to provide David, a senior Stratford homeowner in need, with a new HVAC.
